{"@class": "com.nd.elearning.sdk.resource.gateway.v5.bean.question.QuestionVo", "original_type": 4, "original_sub_type": "questions", "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "id": "3023f969-52b0-4352-8178-5c644f8655a4", "type": 201, "content": {"preview": {"question_big": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/3023f969-52b0-4352-8178-5c644f8655a4@1.pkg/1772597709102/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597710084", "question_small": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/3023f969-52b0-4352-8178-5c644f8655a4@1.pkg/1772597709102/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597710084"}, "identifier": "3023f969-52b0-4352-8178-5c644f8655a4", "test_cases": "", "feedbacks": [{"identifier": "showAnswer", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>本题考查 &ldquo;树立正确的人生目标&rdquo; 中长远目标与近期目标的关系。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">①</span><span>：刘翔的 &ldquo;奥运冠军&rdquo; 梦是长远目标，&ldquo;提升日常训练成绩、在市运会突破&rdquo; 是近期目标，体现了目标的分类，</span><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">①</span><span>正确；</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">②</span><span>：近期目标（如日常训练、市运会成绩）都是为实现长远目标（奥运夺冠）做铺垫，说明近期目标服务于长远目标，</span><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">②</span><span>正确；</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">③</span><span>：刘翔通过逐步实现近期目标最终达成长远目标，表明长远目标的实现依赖于近期目标的积累，</span><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">③</span><span>正确；</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">④</span><span>：&ldquo;只要达成所有近期目标，就一定能实现长远目标&rdquo; 说法绝对，长远目标的实现还受机遇、环境等多种因素影响，</span><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">④</span><span>错误；</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>答案选 A。</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "showHint", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": ""}], "sequnce_number": 1, "description": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">（改编）</span><span>&ldquo;中国飞人&rdquo; 刘翔年少时热爱跨栏，将 &ldquo;成为奥运冠军、为国争光&rdquo; 作为长远目标。为此，他先从提升日常训练成绩做起，一步步在市运会、全运会中突破，最终站上奥运领奖台。这一经历表明（ ）</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">①</span><span>人生目标可分为长远目标与近期目标</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">②</span><span>近期目标的制定应服务于长远目标</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">③</span><span>实现长远目标需要逐步完成近期目标</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">④</span><span>只要达成所有近期目标，就能实现长远目标</span></p></div>", "label": "", "title": "（改编）“中国飞人” 刘翔年少时热爱跨栏，将 “成为奥运冠军、为国争光” 作为长远目标。为此，他先从提升日常训练成绩做起，一步步在市运会、全运会中突破，最终站上奥运领奖台。这一经历表明（ ）①人生目标可分为长远目标与近期目标②近期目标的制定应服务于长远目标③实现长远目标需要逐步完成近期目标④只要达成所有近期目标，就能实现长远目标", "res_type": "$RE0201", "adaptive": false, "timer": {}, "time_dependent": false, "examples": {"responses": [], "feedbacks": [], "items": []}, "responses": [{"identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "1-1", "base_type": "identifier", "cardinality": "single", "corrects": ["A"]}], "location": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/3023f969-52b0-4352-8178-5c644f8655a4@1.pkg/item.json?v=1754984659544", "lang": "", "items": [{"min_choices": 0, "evaluate_result_show": false, "attachments": [], "columns": 1, "type": "choice", "choices_list": [], "associable_hotspots": [], "subtype": "", "children": [], "hide_answer_area": false, "options": [], "orientation": 0, "multiple": false, "raw": false, "titles": [], "rows": 1, "response_identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "0", "max_choices": 1, "gap_imgs": [], "shuffle": false, "choices": [{"identifier": "A", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">①②③</span><span>&nbsp;</span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "B", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">①②④</span><span>&nbsp;</span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "C", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">①③④</span><span>&nbsp;</span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "D", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">②③④</span></p></div>"}], "prompt": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">（改编）</span><span>&ldquo;中国飞人&rdquo; 刘翔年少时热爱跨栏，将 &ldquo;成为奥运冠军、为国争光&rdquo; 作为长远目标。为此，他先从提升日常训练成绩做起，一步步在市运会、全运会中突破，最终站上奥运领奖台。这一经历表明（ ）</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">①</span><span>人生目标可分为长远目标与近期目标</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">②</span><span>近期目标的制定应服务于长远目标</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">③</span><span>实现长远目标需要逐步完成近期目标</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">④</span><span>只要达成所有近期目标，就能实现长远目标</span></p></div>", "object": {"data": "", "width": "1000", "type": "image/png", "params": {"originalImage": "", "blankImage": ""}, "height": "600"}}], "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c87